{"tid":2156362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九月一 全民大三罷","createTime":"2020-08-14T11:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T05:10:43.000Z","uid":207294,"like":38,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"73465dba33fc3fd04bf66cea56a87179dd3a7fd8","tid":2156362,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"街頭抗爭唔係話冇用<br />\n但事實上香港人冇決心好似俄羅斯咁癲<br />\n更何況人哋係戰鬥民族<br />\n<br />\n國安法殺到已經係鐵一般嘅事實<br />\n我哋得返一個最安全 最能表到態<br />\n最有影響嘅行動<br />\n就係<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">全民大三罷</span></span><br />\n我懇請所有工會 學生會<br />\n係依半個月時間好好組織 策劃有關罷工 罷課嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n子彈無論練幾多體能都擋唔到<br />\n罷工罷課罷市只需要乜都唔做便可<br />\n<br />\n我哋冇得再犧牲手足<br />\n少一個就真係少咗<br />\n冇得返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n求下大人罷工罷市<br />\n學生嘅罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baf8cd082d1d0cb9865ee181ff38462f15f9a30","tid":2156362,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"8d2577362232c692ad6266814a35842db3245600","tid":2156362,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dd5e7059afb12554281287619c69b5c94d36ff","tid":2156362,"uid":151324,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:35:30.000Z","msg":"WFH咁少人 再搞罷工 <br />\n黑警睇住地鐵站黎捉手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc7b521ea0349d7841c8d3977eb802bfc83d1a7","tid":2156362,"uid":78184,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"樓主訓醒未？<br />\n正視現實啦"},{"pid":"3fb4a265ffe5c81889cda3258e7626cbd9f00173","tid":2156362,"uid":207294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc7b521ea0349d7841c8d3977eb802bfc83d1a7","tid":2156362,"uid":78184,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"樓主訓醒未？<br />\n正視現實啦"},"citedBy":1,"reply